## Code Review Standards

1. Run tests and lint checks before submitting code: `pnpm lint && pnpm test`
2. Add clear descriptions when creating a Merge Request
3. Code Review focus areas:
   - Code quality and style
   - Test coverage
   - Performance impact
   - Security issues

